'''e-mFire''' is a professional gaming organization based in South Korea. Their team has renamed to {{bl|Kongdoo Monster}}.

==History==
'''e-mFire''' became the new name of the team formerly known as '''[[NaJin e-mFire]]''' in January 2016, when NaJin dropped title sponsorship of the team. Despite this, NaJin continued to operate the team during this period of transition. They competed in the [[LCK/2016 Season/Spring Season|LCK Spring Season]] for five and a half weeks under this name before being sponsored by '''Kongdoo''' in February and renaming to '''[[Kongdoo Monster]]'''.<ref name="kongdoo">[http://www.fomos.kr/esports/news_view?lurl=%2Fesports%2Fnews_list%3Fnews_cate_id%3D13&entry_id=21738 e엠파이어, 콩두 몬스터로 재탄생 한다 (Korean)] ''fomos.kr''</ref>

